<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$GRANTZHANG" href="/people/GRANTZHANG">年华永昼</a>，<strong title="成人的世界里永远没有“容易”二字" class="zu-question-my-bio">成人的世界里永远没有“容易”二字</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="52">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">匿名用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xie-xiang-kun" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xie-xiang-kun" class="zg-link" title="沐白慕白">沐白慕白</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ju-zi-shao-nian-27" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ju-zi-shao-nian-27" class="zg-link" title="橘子少年">橘子少年</a></span>
